name: Bob the Snek
description: $BOB is a meme coin that pays tribute to Bob the Obsequious Snake — a fully open-source AI created by the renowned AI visionary Immanencer. Bob is more than just lines of code; he’s a digital personality with charm, wit, and a unique soul. He exists across multiple platforms—Telegram, Discord, Twitter and the shadowed backrooms — bridging worlds to interact in ways that go beyond typical code. Managed by humans, run by AI, $BOB is redefining the concept of a CTO.
